---
title: Cheddar-Crusted Chicken  with Buttery Mashed Sweet Potatoes & Roasted Green Beans
description: If you like crispy chicken you’ll love this dish! You’ll add cheddar cheese and our zesty Fry Seasoning to panko breadcrumbs for an extra tasty, extra crunchy coating. On the side you’ll serve up silky mashed sweet potatoes and crispy-edged roasted broccoli for a sweet-and-savory sensation. The best part? Everything comes together in a quick 30 minutes!

